&lt;li&gt;Process customs clearances for imports, adhering to all relevant customs regulations and company standard operating procedures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct Importer Security Filing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track and trace shipments to ensure information is up-to-date.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate directly with clients, freight forwarders, and other related parties through email and phone.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage documentation and archive records and documents efficiently.&lt;/li&gt;
