&lt;li&gt;Strong attention to detail and a high level of accuracy in data entry.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work independently as well as collaboratively within a team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to meet strict deadlines and manage multiple tasks simultaneously.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent analytical and problem-solving skills.&lt;/li&gt;
